QuestData.Title: Identify Plant Parts
QuestData.CompletionText: I could still use some more plant parts. With the lakes losing their water, I've a feeling the number of invasive species is on the rise. I need more numbers to back up my theory, however.
QuestData.RewardText: Excellent. Keep bringing me more plant parts if you find any.$B$B<This quest is repeatable up to Honored reputation.>
